{"published time": "2024-03-12T16:31:00+08:00", "images": ["https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/shutterstock_2044440026-scaled.jpg", "https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/1-7.jpg", "https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2-6.jpg", "https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/3-5.jpg", "https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/4-6.jpg", "https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/5-4.jpg", "https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/6-4.jpg", "https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/7-5.jpg", "https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/8-2.jpg"], "content": "<div class=\"single-content\"><figure class=\"post-thumbnail\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" height=\"1443\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-12T16-31-00-08-00/000000.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-12T16-31-00-08-00/000000.jpg\" width=\"2048\"/></figure><!-- .post-thumbnail --><p><strong>In order to receive the privileges provided for by law members of the family of the deceased (deceased) defender or defender of Ukraine, it is necessary to have the appropriate status.</strong></p><p>About this<a href=\"https://t.me/minre_ua/5271\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">informs</a>Ministry of Reintegration.</p><p>In order to acquire the status of a family member of the deceased defender or defender of Ukraine, it is necessary to contact the department for social protection of the population of the district, district in the city of Kyiv of the state administration, the executive body of the city, district in the city council with a statement and relevant documents.</p><div class=\"fotorama--wp\" data-auto=\"false\" data-captiontag=\"dd\" data-columns=\"0\" data-icontag=\"dt\" data-ids=\"550632,550633,550634,550635,550636,550637,550640,550641\" data-itemtag=\"dl\" data-link=\"file\" data-max-width=\"100%\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-size=\"large\" data-width=\"1080\"><div class=\"gallery galleryid-550627 gallery-columns-0 gallery-size-thumbnail\" id=\"gallery-1\"><dl class=\"gallery-item\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-12T16-31-00-08-00/000001.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-12T16-31-00-08-00/000001.jpg\" width=\"150\"/></dt></dl><dl class=\"gallery-item\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-12T16-31-00-08-00/000002.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-12T16-31-00-08-00/000002.jpg\" width=\"150\"/></dt></dl><dl class=\"gallery-item\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-12T16-31-00-08-00/000003.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-12T16-31-00-08-00/000003.jpg\" width=\"150\"/></dt></dl><dl class=\"gallery-item\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-12T16-31-00-08-00/000004.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-12T16-31-00-08-00/000004.jpg\" width=\"150\"/></dt></dl><dl class=\"gallery-item\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-12T16-31-00-08-00/000005.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-12T16-31-00-08-00/000005.jpg\" width=\"150\"/></dt></dl><dl class=\"gallery-item\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-12T16-31-00-08-00/000006.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-12T16-31-00-08-00/000006.jpg\" width=\"150\"/></dt></dl><dl class=\"gallery-item\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-12T16-31-00-08-00/000007.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-12T16-31-00-08-00/000007.jpg\" width=\"150\"/></dt></dl><dl class=\"gallery-item\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" height=\"150\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-12T16-31-00-08-00/000008.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-12T16-31-00-08-00/000008.jpg\" width=\"150\"/></dt></dl></div></div><p>The list of necessary documents and more information can be found in the infographic.</p><p>The categories of persons entitled to obtain such status include:</p><ul><li>families of military personnel (Armed Forces, National Guard and persons who were part of volunteer formations, providing national security and defense);</li><li>families of employees of enterprises, institutions and organizations that carried out national security and defense measures;</li></ul><p>families of persons who died or disappeared.</p><p>Earlier, the Armyinform told in detail that combatants and their families<a href=\"https://armyinform.com.ua/2024/03/02/pilgy-dlya-ubd-u-2024-shho-peredbacheno-ta-yak-otrymaty/\">are eligible for benefits</a>from the state.</p></div>", "source": "https://armyinform.com.ua/2024/03/12/status-chlena-simyi-zagyblogo-zahysnyka-chy-zahysnyczi-ukrayiny-hto-ta-yak-mozhe-otrymaty/", "title": "Status of a family member of a deceased defender or defender of Ukraine: who and how can get", "description": "This was reported by the Ministry of reintegration. To acquire the status of a family member of the dead defender ...", "author": ["Army Inform"], "categories": ["\u041d\u043e\u0432\u0438\u043d\u0438"], "tags": ["\u043f\u0456\u043b\u044c\u0433\u0438"], "source_name": "ArmyInform"}